product_name: Mt.Sapola Microwavable Herbal Compress Body 200g
description: Herbal ball for body has been used as an ancient healing solution for chronic problems such as back pain. Direction: •  Place the herbal compress ball in a steamer for 10 minutes, or microwave for 2 minute at medium power.(Prior heating in microwave, soak the herbal compress ball completely in the water for approximately 1 minute and remove.) •  Take the herbal compress ball out, make sure it's hot but not burning - if not, briefly reheat again and make sure the herbs stay moist enough to not burn. •  Massage your body with the herbal ball until it cools.  Suggest having 2 herbal balls to alternate with the cool one for a more persistent and effective heat treatment. For best result, apply on acupressure points. •   After use, allow the herbal ball to completely cool down before placing it in a cool dry area. This will allow it to last and be used for several more treatments. Caution: - Keep out of reach of children.  - Avoid contact with eyes and ears.  - If skin irritation occurs immediately discontinue use and consult physician.  - External use only. product_name: Torres 10 Imperial Brandy Gran Reserva 38% 1L
description: In 1946, despite a difficult and turbulent time in history, Miguel Torres Carbó created Torres 10, Brandy Torres's flagship brand. The careful selection of grapes, distillation and prolonged aging in top-quality oak casks make Torres 10 a spirit of extraordinary flavor and aroma; characteristics that have made it the most widely sold Brandy Gran Reserva in the world. The aging process uses the Solera System, which gently blends the spirits as they age. This dynamic system allows for consistent, balanced aging, because the vintages blend continuously. Doing so maintains the freshest expression of varietal character as the newly distilled spirit blends with older brandies to acquire depth and structure. The resulting spirit is aromatic, intense, expressive, structured and voluptuous. product_name: Valentino Voce Viva Eau de Parfum 100 ml
description: Roman at heart, Valentino Beauty is a color cool couture brand. VOCE VIVA VALENTINO draws a parallel between the sound of your voice  and the scent of your fragrance. Like a voice, a fragrance is personal, intimate and leaves a trace. The harmony of a radiant floral bouquet made addictive and powerful through an unexpected crystal moss accord. Celebrating every woman’s voice in one declaration: My voice, My strength. VOCE VIVA eau de parfum is an ode to Valentino multi-faceted femininity: - A COLOR NOTE: a colorful and sparkling opening of Italian Bergamot, softened by sweet and juicy mandarin. - A COUTURE NOTE: an opulent bouquet of orange blossom absolute and golden gardenia accord. - A COOL NOTE: an unexpected crystal moss brings a modern intensity to the base becoming wholly addictive by the addition of enveloping vanilla infusion. The bottle transmits the values of Maison Valentino and the VOCE VIVA femininity. A sleek block of glass refracts the light passing through its golden-hued scent allowing a V of light to emerge. Square and notched on the sides, it fits perfectly in the grip of your hand. The emblematic Valentino rockstud highlights the cap and collar, portraying a modern edgy personality. A vibrant red signs this iconic Valentino bottle. Red has always been the iconic color of the house, but as Pierpaolo Piccioli says, “to give a new perspective is a good challenge”. For him red is not only powerful but also a romantic and personal color. The story of VOCE VIVA started with a simple question. What if a perfume could evoke something else than the sense of smell? Imagined as a voice to spread a message around the world, Valentino Voce Viva invites everyone to touch hearts, inspire others and live their dreams. Voce Viva celebrates one of a woman’s most intimate senses, while expressing the Maison’s values of inclusivity and individuality. Voice of a generation, Lady Gaga has inspired millions of people around the world for more than a decade is the ambassadress of VOCE VIVA. With Valentino, the singer shares more than her Italian origins. A symbol of respect for individualities, and for everyone to find their place, Lady Gaga speaks to the same values as those  of Valentino. “I believe today that the true power is to be able share emotions”. Pierpaolo Piccioli, Maison Valentino Creative DirectorRoman at heart, Valentino Beauty is a color cool couture brand. product_name: Wynns, The Gables, Cabernet Sauvingon, Coonawarra, dry, red (screw cap) 0.75L
description: For more than 50 years the heritage listed winery and its famous gables have been a feature of Wynns labels. During that time the gables have become a distinctive mark of exceptional Coonawarra quality. Crafted from small selected parcels of the region’s famous Cabernet Sauvignon blended with premium Shiraz, “The Gables” is designed to partner a diverse range of cuisines.

product_name: Kylie Minogue, Collection, Côtes de Provence, AOC, dry, rosé 0.75L
description: Kylie Minogue Collection Côtes de Provence Rosé is a beautifully pale pink colour with aromatic and bright notes of wild cherries, strawberries and peaches and cream. It is a dry rosé with a fresh long and hugely moreish finish. The Rosé is produced in collaboration with the historic Château Sainte Roseline, situated in the heart of Provence the oldest winemaking region in France and renowned for their world-class rosés.

product_name: Smirnoff Mango & Passionfruit Twist Flavoured Vodka 35% 1L
description: Smirnoff Mango & Passionfruit Twist Flavoured Vodka is bold, tropical and deliciously juicy. Made with unmistakably smooth Smirnoff No. 21 vodka, Smirnoff Mango & Passionfruit Twist is infused with natural mango and passionfruit flavours for a tart and fruity finish. Pairs best with lemonade or pineapple and cranberry juice.

product_name: Bottega, Rosé Gold, brut, rosé, 0.75L
description: Bottega Rose Gold is a pure Pinot Noir sparkling wine. The original packaging really characterises this bottle, transforming it a prestigious gift.

product_name: Kylie Minogue, Prosecco, DOC, extra-dry, rosé 0.75L
description: This sensational Prosecco Rosé is encased in a show-stopping heart embossed bottle. Inside the elegant fizz is every bit as elegant and pretty as the exterior suggests. A gently-sparkling Prosecco with a heavenly scent of fresh strawberries, raspberries and almond blossom. Undeniably thirst-quenching and moreish with a delicate off-dry finish. Kylie Minogue’s debut Prosecco Rosé comes from the prestigious Zonin estate, a family-owned winery spanning seven generations who are the pioneers of premium D.O.C. Prosecco and who celebrated their 200th anniversary earlier this year. Located in the heart of Veneto across the undulating valleys of Gambellara, North West Italy the Zonin Estate stretches across 4,000 hectares and produces arguably some of the best Proseccos in the world.

product_name: Segura Viudas, Reserva Heredad, Penedès, DO, brut, white (gift box) 0.75L
description: Reserva Heredad was created to express style in the world of top of the range sparkling wines. The intention is to offer an elegant and versatile Cava. It is produced only from the finest harvests of Macabeo (67%) and Parellada (33%) grapes, and packaged in a striking had-finished bottle. This is the flagship wine of the Segura Viudas Cava range.

product_name: Danzka Vodka Minipack 40% 4x0.05L gift pack
description: Selection of premium Scandinavian Vodka. DANZKA Original, Apple, Citrus and Cranraz. Perfect small give away to bring back with you.

product_name: Danzka Vodka Fifty 50% 1L
description: Danish design: innovative aluminum bottle that stands out but also has functional benefits.• A premium quality and award winning vodka from Denmark with a Scandinavian heritage.• Premium quality based on a 100% whole grain spirit that has been through a six-column continuous distillation.• Innovative flavors made from only natural flavoring The newest addition to the Danzka Vodka family

product_name: Herpa, Airbus, airplane airbus a380
description: Entry line models for junior collectors.

product_name: Finlandia Vodka Classic 37.5% 1L
description: Finlandia Vodka is produced from entirely natural ingredients including naturally filtered pure glacier spring water that requires no additional treatment or processing, and the finest six-row barley. While growing under the sustained glow of the Midnight Sun, the six-row barley soaks up Finland's pristine air and water, and draws nourishment from its untainted soils, resulting in barley of pure taste and no unnatural oils or odors.

product_name: Finlandia Coconut 37.5% 1L
description: Finlandia Coconut Vodka is a sweet, creamy, buttery Vodka with the nutty taste of coconut, that will bring you right to the tropics - welcome the exotic.

product_name: Maisto Tech R/C, Cyklone Attack 16,5cm
description: The Maisto Tech R/C "Cyklone Attack" is the ultimate off-road vehicle. Thanks to its special rubber tracks, it can easily overcome inclines of up to 40°, make 360° turns and drive over obstacles. There are no limits to the futuristic driving fun and, with a top speed of approx. 3.6 km/h it can also be effortlessly controlled by young experts. The vehicle has a control range of 10m and a 2.4 GHz frequency. Batteries included. (4x AA for the vehicle and 2x AAA for the remote control).

product_name: Grey Goose Vodka 40% 1L
description: Grey Goose is a premium flavoured vodka, born from an extraordinary passion for spirit-making. It is created using only the finest French ingredients – the highest-grade wheat and pristine limestone-filtered spring water. It is a spirit of uncommon brilliance, unrivalled craftsmanship and signature smoothness and is an excellent choice as a gift.

product_name: Maisto Model Car Bugatti Chiron 42sec.
description: Model Car type Bugatti Chiron 42sec. World record Car; scale 1:24; metallic black with tuned details in turquoise; opening doors; length approx. 18,5 cm; Windowbox; Material: Die-Cast with plastic parts

product_name: Grey Goose Vodka 40% 0.2L
description: From field to bottle every aspect of the creation of Grey Goose is focused on crafting the worlds best tasting vodka. With the finest French ingredients, soft winter wheat and Gensac spring water and a unique production process to ensure its distinctive character and unparalleled taste. Serve in a Grey Goose Le Fizz or simply on the rocks.

product_name: Maisto Tech, vw samba
description: The 11 cm high Power Racer VW T1 Samba from Maisto Tech R/C guarantees driving fun for young and old. The car has working headlights, a frequency of 2.4 GHz, a range of about 10 m and an integrated battery that can be charged via the included USB cable. The car can be operated using Bluetooth and the Maisto cell phone app. It can be controlled both by pressing buttons in the app and by moving the smartphone. With its approx. 6 km/h, the Volkswagen is already suitable for children from the age of 6.

product_name: La Collina Toscana Grinder Sicilian white salt 600g
description: Big Grinder with Sicilian white Salt. The grinder is with an inner aluminium rust-free bar. It's a refilable grinder with adjustable grinding from fine to coarse. The mechanism is in ceramic. Ideal for any kind of dish.

product_name: Mumm Champagne Cordon Rouge Brut 0.75L
description: Made from a rich palette of more than 120 villages representing all the diversity of the Champagne region of France, Mumm Cordon Rouge is the signature cuvee of Maison Mumm. This exceptional brut champagne blends Mumm’s signature grape variety, Pinot Noir from the Montagne de Reims and Aube; with Chardonnay from the Côte des Blancs, Sézannais, Vitryat and Aube; and Meunier from the Marne and Ardre valleys and the Montagne de Reims

product_name: Intex, Intex-Wet Set, water ball Lively

The colorful balls with a diameter of 51 cm are made of a 0.18 mm thick, robust material that does not hurt if you are hit by the ball. The water balls are available in three different designs: with funny fish, colorful pineapple and summer fruit print. Suitable for children from 3 years.

Whether they contain roasted hazelnuts, fine marzipan, delicate praline, crispy cornflakes, crunchy organic shortbread biscuits or rich milk chocolate, these tiny squares are every bit as tasty as their 100g role models. Indulge in the harmony ofyogurt and berries with our delicious Ritter Sport Choco Cubes Fruity Yogurt Mix . The Ritter Sport Choco Cube bag contains a mix of20 Choco Cubes and is perfect for sharing with family and friends. If only they weren’t always polished off so quickly …

product_name: Lindt Lindor Gift Box assorted chocolates 287g
description: Discover Lindor and enjoy a moment that is yours. The LINDOR Assorted Gift Box is the perfect gift. The exquisitely wrapped box, complete with beautiful ribbon and bow, is sure to impress your loved ones.

product_name: Guylian Master Selection 185g
